          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Absolute values of  integrated  cross  sections  were",
                " obtained from relative yields using normalization to",
                " the averaged experimental photoneutron (gamma,n),",
                " (gamma,2n) and (gamma,3n) reaction cross sections.",
                "Those were a rough estimations of integration reaction",
                " cross section as reaction yield measured for definite",
                " end-point energy EN-max delayed by integrated photon",
                " spectrum and multiplyed by the difference between",
                " EN-max and reaction threshold."
